ZH: 我们明天晚上要去参加一个公司的晚会。
EN: We are going to attend a company party tomorrow night.

ZH: 他们家每年都会举办一次盛大的晚会。
EN: Their family hosts a grand party every year.

ZH: 晚会上有很多有趣的游戏和节目。
EN: There are many fun games and performances at the party.

ZH: 我很期待这个晚会，因为会有很多朋友来参加。
EN: I am looking forward to the party because many friends will attend.

ZH: 这场晚会的主题是传统文化。
EN: The theme of this party is traditional culture.

ZH: 你有兴趣来参加我们的晚会吗？
EN: Are you interested in attending our party?

ZH: 我昨天晚上在晚会上结识了很多新朋友。
EN: I made many new friends at the party last night.

ZH: 晚会的食物特别好吃，我吃了很多。
EN: The food at the party was delicious, I ate a lot.

ZH: 这个晚会需要穿正装吗？
EN: Do we need to dress formally for this party?

ZH: 晚会现场会有音乐表演。
EN: There will be live music performances at the party.

ZH: 我们将在酒店举办晚会。
EN: We will host the party at the hotel.

ZH: 提前预订座位可以确保你参加晚会。
EN: Reserving a seat in advance can ensure your attendance at the party.

ZH: 请务必准时到达晚会场地。
EN: Please make sure to arrive at the party venue on time.

ZH: 这场晚会的门票很抢手，赶紧买一个吧。
EN: The tickets for this party are selling fast, hurry up and get one.

ZH: 晚会上会有抽奖活动，你有机会赢得奖品。
EN: There will be a lucky draw at the party, you have a chance to win prizes.

ZH: 晚会结束后，我们可以去附近的酒吧继续聚会。
EN: After the party ends, we can go to a nearby bar to continue the gathering.

ZH: 请遵守晚会的礼仪规定，尊重他人。
EN: Please follow the etiquette rules of the party and respect others.

ZH: 晚会将持续到午夜，届时会有烟火表演。
EN: The party will last until midnight, there will be a fireworks display.

ZH: 我们将在露天花园举办晚会，期待与你共度美好时光。
EN: We will host the party in the outdoor garden, looking forward to spending a good time with you.
